channel.title: Unexpected type errors
channel.description:
Hi everyone, I'm trying to add a hide and seek minigame to my server (The one that mrjad created) but I get 2 unexpected type errors Here are my errors: [code] client.java:17792: unexpected type required: variable found : value isInHS() = true; ^ client.java:17802: unexpected type required: variable found : value isInHS() = false; ^ 2 errors Finished! Press any key to continue . . . [/code] And here is what i declared: (its in client.java) [code] public boolean isInHS() { if((absX >= 2366 && absX <= 2433 && absY >= 3070 && absY <=3137)) return true; else return false; }[/code]
Im using pk planet v3 and this is a 317

public boolean isInHS() { if((absX >= 2366 && absX <= 2433 && absY >= 3070 && absY <=3137)) return true; else return false; }

public boolean isInHS() { if((absX >= 2366 && absX <= 2433 && absY >= 3070 && absY <=3137)) { return true; else return false; } }
